headline: HOKA Unveils 2025 Global Brand Campaign: Together We Fly Higher
summary: GOLETA, Calif., July 10, 2025--HOKA®, a division of Deckers Brands (NYSE: DECK) introduces its 2025 global brand campaign, "Together We Fly Higher," celebrating the unifying power of running in bringing people together to push further. The campaign underscores how support fuels individual progress and the importance of community in helping runners succeed. The campaign will roll out globally across out-of-home, social, digital, and connected TV national video spots.
